3. Important correction: biology lags hard

This part matters:

Culture and tech change in years
Biology changes in hundreds to thousands of years

So right now we’re in a mismatch:
	•	Ancient brain
	•	Modern environment

That gap creates:
	•	Anxiety
	•	Overstimulation
	•	Dopamine loops
	•	Identity instability

